00:02:50.440 --> 00:02:52.000
It's interesting as the apostle Paul,

00:02:52.000 --> 00:02:53.600
those to whom he is writing,

00:02:53.600 --> 00:02:55.399
he refers to them as being saints,

00:02:55.399 --> 00:02:59.240
and we find that he addresses in the opening statements

00:02:59.240 --> 00:03:01.600
of Ephesians chapter number one in these first

00:03:01.600 --> 00:03:04.960
several verses, he deals with the important subject,

00:03:04.960 --> 00:03:07.639
vital subject of redemption.

00:03:07.639 --> 00:03:10.880
And this subject is so vital, it's so important.

00:03:10.880 --> 00:03:14.240
In fact, because we find that the apostle Paul,

00:03:14.240 --> 00:03:17.880
